General.Name: Archicom S.A.
General.Description: Archicom S.A. engages in the real estate activities in Poland. It is also involved in the construction, rental, and sale of commercial and residential real estate properties; buying and selling of owned real estate properties; implementation of building construction projects; and leasing of intellectual properties, as well as provides financial services. The company was founded in 1986 and is headquartered in Wroclaw, Poland. Archicom S.A. is a subsidiary of Echo Investment S.A.
